Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
JSimpleDB Ant Tasks Ant tasks for use with JSimpleDB.
JSimpleDB Application Classes JSimpleDB classes supporting command line applications that utilize JSimpleDB.
JSimpleDB CLI Classes JSimpleDB classes supporting command line interfaces.
JSimpleDB CLI Telnet Classes Telnet server for the JSimpleDB Command Line Interface (CLI).
JSimpleDB CLI Application JSimpleDB Command Line Interface (CLI) executable application.
JSimpleDB Core API Classes JSimpleDB core API classes which provide objects, fields, indexes, queries, and schema management on top of a key/value store.
JSimpleDB Demo Classes JSimpleDB demonstration classes.
JSimpleDB GUI Application JSimpleDB Graphical User Interface (GUI) executable application.
JSimpleDB Array Key/Value Store JSimpleDB "array" key/value store implementations.
JSimpleDB Berkeley DB Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on Berkeley DB Java Edition.
JSimpleDB CockroachDB Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on CockroachDB.
JSimpleDB FoundationDB Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on FoundationDB.
JSimpleDB LevelDB Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on LevelDB.
JSimpleDB MySQL Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store based on MySQL.
JSimpleDB Raft Key/Value Store JSimpleDB distributed, linearizable ACID compliant key/value store implementation based on the Raft consensus algorithm.
JSimpleDB RocksDB Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on RocksDB.
JSimpleDB Simple Key/Value Store Classes A couple of simplistic JSimpleDB key/value store implementations.
JSimpleDB Google Cloud Spanner Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on Google Cloud Spanner.
JSimpleDB SQL Database Key/Value Store Support for JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on SQL databases.
JSimpleDB SQLite Key/Value Store JSimpleDB key/value store implementation based on SQLite.
JSimpleDB Key/Value Store Test Classes JSimpleDB unit test classes for key/value store implementations.
JSimpleDB Key/Value Store Base Classes JSimpleDB classes relating to the key/value store API.
JSimpleDB Main Classes JSimpleDB classes that map Java model classes onto the core API.
JSimpleDB Maven Plugin Maven plugin for use with JSimpleDB.
JSimpleDB Parsing Classes JSimpleDB classes for parsing Java expressions.
JSimpleDB Spring Classes JSimpleDB classes for the Spring Framework.
JSimpleDB Test Classes JSimpleDB unit test support classes.
JSimpleDB Utility Classes Common utility classes used by JSimpleDB.
JSimpleDB Vaadin Classes JSimpleDB classes supporting Vaadin applications.
